===財產來源===
根據墨西哥當局的說法，葉真理的財產主要來自販毒活動。可是，葉真理本人卻指出這些財物都是被{{tsl|en|Secretariat of Labor and Social Welfare|墨西哥勞工部}}部長，[[墨西哥国家行动党|墨西哥国家行动党]]党員{{tsl|en|Javier Lozano Alarcón|哈維爾·洛薩諾·阿拉爾孔}}強迫放置在家<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2007-07-02-mexico-millions-seized_N.htm |title=Mexico accuses drug suspect of blackmail |publisher=Usatoday.Com |date=2007-07-02 |accessdate=2010-10-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/10/28/AR2008102801364.html| title=Mexico, the DEA, and the Case of Zhenli Ye Gon| author= Jorge Carrasco| work=The Washington Post| date= October 29, 2008 }}</ref>。

